sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.services.listeners

Interface ListenerService.Builder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractListenerService.AbstractBuilder
    Enclosing interface:
    ListenerService

    public static interface ListenerService.Builder
    A builder for creating listener service instances.

    Builder instances can be reused, it is safe to call build() multiple times to build multiple listener services in series.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
